\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
\Cov(\sum_{i=1}^{k}w_{i}\widehat{X}_{i},Z) & = & \Cov\left(\sum_{i=1}^{k}w_{i}\widehat{X}_{i},\sum_{i=1}^{k}v_{i}\widehat{X}_{i}\right)=w^{T}\Xi v.
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

Standardize to find the correlation 
\begin_inset Formula $w^{T}\Xi v/\sqrt{w^{T}\Xi w}$
\end_inset

, and the squared correlation is 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega'=(w^{T}\Xi v)^{2}/w^{T}\Xi w$
\end_inset

.
 This completes point (i).
 
